{"tid":2412560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"體育館看更逼人用安心出行","createTime":"2021-02-18T06:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T06:39:05.000Z","uid":303083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"426104d62218b6c81f798bcec07af320753f465e","tid":2412560,"uid":303083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"今個星期二年初五想入西貢體育館，點知見到成班人係外面入唔到去，原來個廢老看要人一定要下載安心出行，我地話未下載想寫紙仔佢都唔比。話紙仔只係方便老人家，後生要用翻apps。然後拗咗幾分鐘先比我地寫紙仔，又話寫完電話資料再打比我地等我地電話響咗先放人入去。咁樣又算唔算盜取市民資料？？又話年初七先生效？？好想瘋狂投訴佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477eca23ad347dbfa3c2ee6e8a5570da3e2682ef","tid":2412560,"uid":301529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:06:52.000Z","msg":"遲啲拉埋你添呀，大聲啲都侮辱公職人員"},{"pid":"6a302772e4cc75671cb0d1a4dc28a51cfeb3a036","tid":2412560,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"政府地方係麻煩啲㗎啦"},{"pid":"84fd5b19299de271a502b2d0841e65f2853d8fd0","tid":2412560,"uid":34553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:10:06.000Z","msg":"今日咪初七"},{"pid":"fee91b2fc7be8f27a32f9c318a1bf52481a1bceb","tid":2412560,"uid":303083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84fd5b19299de271a502b2d0841e65f2853d8fd0","tid":2412560,"uid":34553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:10:06.000Z","msg":"今日咪初七"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"前兩日去架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30ca31d6fea6d0ae4af5d9e8496e34f436626ad","tid":2412560,"uid":303083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a302772e4cc75671cb0d1a4dc28a51cfeb3a036","tid":2412560,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"政府地方係麻煩啲㗎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:18:45.000Z","msg":"遲早街都唔比出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46575313aa189a2cb4bdd3182e